{"tid":2089614,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國假髮年賺2千億　美媒：恐來自新疆再教育營","createTime":"2020-07-01T18:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T07:36:24.000Z","uid":53062,"like":250,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"3f662182a68c6e2574995760812c02287fdbfd3e","tid":2089614,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T18:24:03.000Z","msg":"中國為全球最大的髮製品出口國，涵蓋全球8成以上頭髮製成的相關產品，像是假髮和假睫毛，該產業受到中國當局鼓勵，短短10年間，產值從1億美元（約新台幣30億元）飆漲到67億美元（約新台幣2,010億元）。不過，近日有美媒披露，這些髮製品的原始原料很可能是來自新疆再教育營被拘禁的維吾爾女性。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，人權研究員伊桑古特曼（Ethan Gutmann）提到，中國原始頭髮的產量比起2017年，足足增加了78%，斷言「肯定來自那些維吾爾女性」，頭髮剃了還會再長出來，這些維吾爾人儼然成了中國當局的「補充物資」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/amp/20200602edi034/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.mg%2Fstory%2Famp%2F20200602edi034%2F&d=Ia4lQUE8yf8cF0bf%2B23B9YkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=28de7077\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/amp/20200602edi034/</a>"},{"pid":"68458a3d8748c057aa94f15bc4156e4d26ff7f66","tid":2089614,"uid":53062,"like":53,"dislike":2,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T18:26:38.000Z","msg":"美國今日截獲到13噸懷疑新疆集中營的假髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a57.foxnews.com/static.foxnews.com/foxnews.com/content/uploads/2020/07/640/320/china-hair-products-4-CBP.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa57.foxnews.com%2Fstatic.foxnews.com%2Ffoxnews.com%2Fcontent%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F640%2F320%2Fchina-hair-products-4-CBP.jpg%3Fve%3D1%26tl%3D1&h=a4d54acc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/politics/feds-seize-tons-of-products-from-suspected-forced-labor-in-china.amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Ffeds-seize-tons-of-products-from-suspected-forced-labor-in-china.amp&d=Ia4lQUE8yf8cF0bf%2B23B9YkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=e463c726\" data-ef-url=\"https://